Package: gameday
Title: Let R tell you if your NHL team has a game today
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: "Yi Sui <yi.sui@math.ubc.ca> [aut, cre]"
Description: Query live.nhle.com to check if your NHL team is listed on the
    teams that play today
